settings.title: We cook and pack your order for the week
settings.text: We handcraft each dish with care, ensuring a fresh and flavourful experience with every order.

settings.title: Enjoy your meals
settings.text: Enjoy your hand picked selection of meals throughout the next week!

settings.title: Choose Your Meal
settings.text: Select from our enticing menu of delevtable dishes, tailored to your preferences and dietary needs. (Order before thursday 8am AEST)

settings.title: We deliver your meals
settings.text: We deliver the meals to you on the Sunday (You can opt for Monday if you are in Sydney Metro)

settings.sub_title: FROM OUR KITCHEN TO YOUR HOME
settings.title: How it Works
settings.desc: Discover the simplicity of our process and start enjoying our delicious dishes in just a few easy steps.

settings.question: How is my order packed?
settings.answer: Our meals are packed in a thermal sleeved box with ice pack and can stay cool for up to 6 hours.

settings.question: How long do the meals last?
settings.answer:
When stored correctly, our meals have a best before of 8 days. Excluding meals with fresh produce Eg: tabouli, guacamole, musakhan.
Please refer to the best before label on each pack.

settings.question: Are your meals halal?
settings.answer: All our ingredients are 100% Halal approved â€“ We purchase only hand-slaughtered quality meats.

settings.question: Can I pick up my order?
Where do you deliver & how much?
settings.answer: We deliver to Sydney Metro and interstate.

settings.question: How do I subscribe to your meal service?
settings.answer: Subscribing is easy. Just choose your favourite meals from our subscription page and weâ€™ll take care of the rest.

settings.question: Can I change my meal choices with my subscription?
settings.answer:
This will depend on the cut off time and the expected delivery date for your order as the meals are prepared shortly after the cut off time. Please contact us directly if you have any urgent requests and we will see how we can accommodate.

For subscriptions, you can cancel at any time and start a new subscription with different products. However, any orders placed and processed will remain, and the changes will take effect at the next payment cycle.
